OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAfghanistan: Taliban       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fannounce new rules for     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffemale students            
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Afghan universities will be segregated 
OL,6, by gender, and a new dress code will be
OL,7, introduced, the Taliban has said.      
OL,9,FHigher Education Minister Abdul Baqi   
OL,10,FHaqqani indicated women would be       
OL,11,Fallowed to study, but not alongside    
OL,12,Fmen.                                   
OL,14,FHe also announced a review of the      
OL,15,Fsubjects students would be taught.     
OL,17,FWomen and girls were banned from       
OL,18,Fschools and universities under Taliban 
OL,19,Frule between 1996 and 2001.            
